      "content": "That makes sense. Can you get a bit more specific on the hair aspect? Like, for employees who might have more natural or textured hair, or even people who wear religious headwear, how should they approach styling to make sure they still fit that 'understated' and 'authoritative' look you mentioned? I want to make sure they don't look too casual or out of place in the boardroom.",
